title: GSM2462948
organism_ch1: liver, fed normal CRF-1 chow for 12 weeks
growth_protocol_ch1: 7-week-old C57BL/6J male mice were fed NC (CRF-1) or CL diet (60% calories from fat, 1.25% cholesterol, and 0.5% sodium cholate), CL diet containing 0.02% astaxanthin, or CL diet containing 0.02% vitamin E for 12 weeks.
molecule_ch1: Mice were maintained on a 12/12-h light/dark cycle and were given free access to food and water.
label_ch1: The liver tissues were collected after 2-h fasting and snap-frozen in liquid nitrogen.  Total RNA was isolated from frozen liver samples using a GenElute Mammalian Total RNA Miniprep Kit (Sigma-Aldrich Japan, Tokyo, Japan) according to the manufacturer’s instructions.
taxid_ch1: The fragmented biotin-labeled aRNA was synthesized from the total RNA of each mouse using the GeneChip® 3′ IVT Express Kit (Affymetrix Japan KK, Tokyo, Japan).
scan_protocol: Fragmented cRNA were hybridized to an array (Mouse Genome 430 2.0 array, Affymetrix) at 45°C for 16 h.
description: After hybridization, the gene chips were washed and stained using a GeneChip Fluidics Station 450 (Affymetrix) and then scanned (GeneChip Scanner; Affymetrix) with the GeneChip Operation Software Ver. 1.4 (Affymetrix).
data_processing: Gene expression data from the liver after 12 week feeding of normal CRF-1 chow
platform_id: Data analysis was performed with a GeneChip Operating Software (Ver. 1.4) using Affymetrix default analysis settings and global scaling as normalization method.
contact_address: Food Research Institute, National Agriculture and Food Research Organization

scan_protocol: Fragmented cRNA were hybridized to an array (Mouse Genome 430 2.0 array, Affymetrix) at 45°C for 16 h.
description: After hybridization, the gene chips were washed and stained using a GeneChip Fluidics Station 450 (Affymetrix) and then scanned (GeneChip Scanner; Affymetrix) with the GeneChip Operation Software Ver. 1.4 (Affymetrix).
data_processing: Gene expression data from the liver after 12 week feeding of CL diet containing 0.02% vitamin E
platform_id: Data analysis was performed with a GeneChip Operating Software (Ver. 1.4) using Affymetrix default analysis settings and global scaling as normalization method.
contact_address: Food Research Institute, National Agriculture and Food Research Organization
